# i18n Guide

- Dictionaries live in [`src/i18n/lang`](mdc:src/i18n/lang/): `en.json`, `ja-JP.json`, `zh-CN.json`.
- The i18n bootstrap is in [`src/i18n/i18n.jsx`](mdc:src/i18n/i18n.jsx). Use provided helpers/contexts to read the active locale.
- UI language switching is handled by [`LangSwitcher.jsx`](mdc:src/i18n/LangSwitcher.jsx).
- Add new keys consistently across all dictionaries; avoid hard-coded strings in pages/components.
- When adding new UI, reference dictionary keys and ensure fallbacks for missing keys.
